WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
My name is Fulton Skikos.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.200
I was an RA last year at the Yak Community Building 172d, or Chikukunitch.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.500
If I'm being honest, I didn't really enjoy being an RA at all.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:14.200
It was very difficult.

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:18.300
Each day came with various challenges that I just really wasn't up for.

00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:22.000
I had to help this one freshman who got back from a party.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.700
She was throwing up for hours and hours.

00:00:25.700 --> 00:00:29.500
It ended up in the sink, which is pretty nasty.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:33.500
I had to personally clean it up.

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:38.300
I didn't want the housekeeper to come in and be like, "What the hell is this?"

00:00:38.300 --> 00:00:43.900
I really think that Cal Poly should do a better job of fixing this program.

00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:48.300
They should make it more rewarding for the people who dedicate their year.

00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:52.200
People are looking out for the freshmen, and in return I don't get crap.

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:55.200
Except for free housing and a free meal plan.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:57.000
Even that was, I mean, the food here sucks.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.267
The biggest highlight was handing out scented pencils for the check-ins.
